snippet.title: JumpStart Adventures 4th Grade: Haunted Island Walkthrough - Part 1
snippet.description:
JumpStart Adventures 4th Grade: Haunted Island Walkthrough
Part 1

JumpStart Adventures 4th Grade: Haunted Island is an educational game created by Knowledge Adventure. It was created in December 2, 1996. However, this game was discontinued in 2000. This game was a personal computer game in Knowledge Adventure's JumpStart series of educational software intended, as the title indicates, to teach a fourth grade curriculum. This version of the game was released in 1996, but was retired from the line in 2000 and replaced with JumpStart Adventures 4th Grade: Sapphire Falls, presumably due to it being deemed too scary for an educational game, but not for Halloween! LOL
